PN,42101
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1776963955
OL,3,CRapist jailed for life after
OL,4,Cdeliberately infecting men with HIV
OL,6,FA man who deliberately infected
OL,7,Fvulnerable and inexperienced sexual
OL,8,Fpartners, including a boy of 15, with
OL,9,FHIV has been jailed for at least 23
OL,10,Fyears.
OL,12,FAdam Hall, 43, of Washington, Tyne and
OL,13,FWear hid his HIV status from partners,
OL,14,Ffailed to take medication to keep his
OL,15,Fviral load low, then had unprotected
OL,16,Fsex with men, sometimes raping them.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,422,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1776963955
OL,3,CRapist jailed for life after
OL,4,Cdeliberately infecting men with HIV
OL,6,FHe was convicted of five counts of
OL,7,Frape and seven counts of causing
OL,8,Fgrievous bodily harm - by deliberately
OL,9,Finfecting younger partners with HIV
OL,10,Fafter meeting them in bars in the
OL,11,FNewcastle area or on the dating app
OL,12,FGrindr.
OL,14,FHall's victims were aged from late 20s
OL,15,Fdown to just 15, with the schoolboy
OL,16,Ffinding out he had contracted HIV in a
OL,17,Fphone call from health professionals
OL,18,Fmoments after he stepped off a school
OL,19,Fbus.
OL,21,FTwo of his victims were just 17 and 18.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,422,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1776963955
OL,3,CRapist jailed for life after
OL,4,Cdeliberately infecting men with HIV
OL,6,FJudge Edward Bindloss deemed Hall
OL,7,F"dangerous" before jailing him for
OL,8,Flife with a minimum term of 23 years
OL,9,Fand 42 days.
OL,11,FThe 15-year-old victim, now an adult,
OL,12,Ftold how he was walking home from the
OL,13,Fschool bus when he received a call
OL,14,Ffrom a sexual health nurse explaining
OL,15,Fthat test results showed he was HIV
OL,16,Fpositive.
OL,18,FThe survivor's words in the below clip
OL,19,Fare voiced by an actor:
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,422,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1776963955
OL,3,CRapist jailed for life after
OL,4,Cdeliberately infecting men with HIV
OL,6,FHe said: "Everything shattered,
OL,7,Feverything went numb.
OL,9,F"I was mortified, not only at the
OL,10,Fsituation, at myself. How has this
OL,11,Fhappened to me, I felt like I was
OL,12,Fsinking."
OL,14,FA third victim said: "The whole thing
OL,15,Fis so unfair, he knew he was infected,
OL,16,Fand he thought he could get away with
OL,17,Finfecting me, that he was immune from
OL,18,Fany consequences.
OL,26,@nD@JOUqD@AOUtD@IO]vD@VOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,422,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1776963955
OL,3,CRapist jailed for life after
OL,4,Cdeliberately infecting men with HIV
OL,6,F"He didn't even give me the option to
OL,7,Ftake any pre or post-HIV exposure
OL,8,Ftreatment.
OL,10,FOne of the victims said: "I blame
OL,11,Fmyself for letting the monster in."
OL,13,FAfter a four-month trial at Newcastle
OL,14,FCrown Court, Hall became just the
OL,15,Fsecond person in the country to be
OL,16,Fconvicted of deliberately infecting
OL,17,Fother people with HIV.
OL,19,FHall denied the charges, even claiming
OL,20,Fsome of his victims wanted to be
OL,21,Finfected with HIV.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@ZOUsD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,422,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1776963955
OL,3,CRapist jailed for life after
OL,4,Cdeliberately infecting men with HIV
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FHe was known on the Newcastle gay sex
OL,12,Fscene, worked in bars and at a
OL,13,FTyneside sex shop, and had even tried
OL,14,Fto set up a charity for people with
OL,15,FHIV.
OL,17,FHe was diagnosed with HIV in 2010 and
OL,18,Fcould have kept his viral load low
OL,19,Fwith modern treatments.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,422,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1776963955
OL,3,CRapist jailed for life after
OL,4,Cdeliberately infecting men with HIV
OL,6,FBut in 2016, medical professionals
OL,7,Fbecame concerned he was not adhering
OL,8,Fto his treatment, making him
OL,9,Finfectious to others he slept with.
OL,11,FDespite being warned, Hall had
OL,12,Funprotected sex with men between 2016
OL,13,Fand 2023, in some cases raping them.
OL,15,FProsecutors were sure Hall intended to
OL,16,Fspread HIV, although he continued to
OL,17,Fdeny it.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,422,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1776963955
OL,3,CRapist jailed for life after
OL,4,Cdeliberately infecting men with HIV
OL,6,FCraig Hassall KC, defending, said Hall
OL,7,Ftold the probation officer who
OL,8,Fcompiled a pre-sentence report "he
OL,9,Ffeels sick at the thought that he had
OL,10,Ftransferred HIV to others".
OL,12,FHe added: "He maintains he did not do
OL,13,Fso intentionally."
OL,15,FOutside court, senior prosecutor Amy
OL,16,FDixon said: "When we looked at all of
OL,17,Fthat surrounding evidence in relation
OL,18,Fto his sexual activity with the victim-
OL,19,Fsurvivors, it was clear that he'd
OL,20,Fintended to pass on this virus.
OL,26,@pD@`OUrD@ZO]tD@KOUuD@RO]xD@MOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,422,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1776963955
OL,3,CRapist jailed for life after
OL,4,Cdeliberately infecting men with HIV
OL,6,F"He hadn't just been reckless."
OL,8,FDetective Chief Inspector Emma Smith
OL,9,Fsaid: "He's shown absolutely no
OL,10,Fremorse.
OL,12,F"He's never apologised for his
OL,13,Fbehaviour and we've interviewed him on
OL,14,Fa number of occasions.
OL,16,F"He provided a prepared statement via
OL,17,Fhis legal representative, and then no
OL,18,Fcomment answers.
OL,26,@nD@AOUnD@_O]qD@GOUtD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,422,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1776963955
OL,3,CRapist jailed for life after
OL,4,Cdeliberately infecting men with HIV
OL,6,F"He came across as quite arrogant,
OL,7,Fquite dismissive, and I would say that
OL,8,Fthat continued into the trial.
OL,10,F"In fact, he actually suggested that
OL,11,Fsome of the victims wanted him to pass
OL,12,Fon HIV to them, which is absolutely
OL,13,Fnot the case.
OL,15,F"There was witness testimony to say
OL,16,Fthat he'd been bragging that the
OL,17,Fpolice investigation wouldn't go
OL,18,Fanywhere and nothing was going to
OL,19,Fhappen to him."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUwD@AOU{D@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
