OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,422,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1776963955
OL,3,CRapist jailed for life after
OL,4,Cdeliberately infecting men with HIV
OL,6,FThe detective said the criminal case
OL,7,Fwas "complex" and involved 35,000
OL,8,Fhours of officers' time, including 450
OL,9,Fstatements and 37 witnesses who gave
OL,10,Fevidence.
OL,12,FThe case was further complicated by
OL,13,Fthe difficulty of some of the medical
OL,14,Fevidence which was used to show the
OL,15,Fstrain of HIV which victims contracted
OL,16,Fwas consistent with Hall's, and it
OL,17,Finvolved exploring the victims' sexual
OL,18,Fhistory with other partners.
OL,26,@oD@EOUoD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,422,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42112
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1776963955
OL,3,CRapist jailed for life after
OL,4,Cdeliberately infecting men with HIV
OL,6,FHall was not charged with underage sex
OL,7,Fwith the 15-year-old as it would need
OL,8,Fto be proved that he knew the boy was
OL,9,Funderage.
OL,11,FHall was brought to court from prison
OL,12,Fwhere he was held on remand, but
OL,13,Fdeclined to leave his cell and was
OL,14,Fsentenced in his absence.
OL,16,FJudge Bindloss said: "Refusal to
OL,17,Fattend today is entirely in keeping
OL,18,Fwith the indifference you have shown
OL,19,Fto the suffering of others."
OL,26,@xD@VOU{D@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G12/13
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
