OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,422,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42113
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1776963955
OL,3,CRapist jailed for life after
OL,4,Cdeliberately infecting men with HIV
OL,6,FOf the victims, the judge said: "All
OL,7,Fwere young men, all had their futures
OL,8,Ftaken away, all deliberately because
OL,9,Fof you."
OL,11,FHall was also jailed for drug dealing
OL,12,Fand failing to reveal his PIN to
OL,13,Fpolice.
OL,15,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,16,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,17,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,18,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,19,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,20,Fbelow...
OL,26,@nD@aOUqD@HO]
